<paragraph pageId="38" pageNumber="39">
<bibRefCitation author="Breure, ASH" journalOrPublisher="ZooKeys" pageId="84" pageNumber="85" pagination="1 - 70" title="Annotated type catalogue of the Bothriembryontidae and Odontostomidae (Mollusca, Gastropoda, Orthalicoidea) in the Natural History Museum, London." url="10.3897/zookeys.182.2720" volume="182" year="2012">Breure and Ablett (2012)</bibRefCitation>
